    partOfSpeech v
    synonyms (control)
  entry
    definition "attach or append a legal verification to (a pleading or petition)"
    id oewn-01014404-v
    partOfSpeech v
  entry
    definition "to declare or affirm solemnly and formally as true"
    examples ("Before God I swear I am innocent")
    id oewn-01013058-v
    partOfSpeech v
    synonyms (affirm assert avow aver swan swear)
